scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 2-211 comprise the full Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, starting with the heading 'SCHEDULE to the 2002 ISDA Master Agreement' and including all the 'Parts' (1-7) and their provisions, ending with the parties' signatures. The content before line 2 is exhibit labeling, and after line 211 is a page break. No CSA annexes or standard pre-print text are included in this span.
